{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"139000-de-wolk-die-op-reis-ging","title":"De wolk die op reis ging","description":"Op een dag ging Wolk op reis. Wie komt hij onderweg tegen?","language":"Dutch","langCode":"nl","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Katja van der Schans"],"illustrators":["Ajit Narayan","Sangeetha Kadur"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/139000-de-wolk-die-op-reis-ging"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43560/size3/94a17f5bd47f25ab86a70b58d7194a89.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43560/size6/94a17f5bd47f25ab86a70b58d7194a89.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43546/size6/b9d1f0565b3e428dd5b7bc2034078dfe.jpg","text":"Wolk ging op reis.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43547/size6/14b22c5c821edf61b6d9aa8b1c299f3c.jpg","text":"'Wat ben je mooi' zei Wolk tegen Pauw.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43548/size6/592774ce783deb843e5f770108aa1d6f.jpg","text":"'Hey! Wij kwamen om te spelen!' riepen kinderen naar Wolk.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43549/size6/f80018073d927af1c01215053e44e961.jpg","text":"'Kom op dan! Laten we spelen' zei Wolk, en hij begon op de kinderen te regenen.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43550/size6/f2acf39db258539606ca39fcebb931d8.jpg","text":"Even later bedacht Wolk dat hij op reis was. Stilletjes ging hij weer weg.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43552/size6/90df2ae892c10509f54591a7340d65e2.jpg","text":"Een boer wachtte op Wolk.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43553/size6/3f38c250e8e314bc58a73a54b6a11570.jpg","text":"Hij zei tegen Wolk: 'Als het regent op het veld, zal ik rijst oogsten.'","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43554/size6/7aefde5f6f9858a58eadf4eaafec494b.jpg","text":"'Hier, kijk eens aan' zei Wolk terwijl hij begon te regenen.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43555/size6/f37bef7257d5adfdfb8b13b17a06d4c6.jpg","text":"De boer oogstte de rijst.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43556/size6/90d4b6ef86ca58b3a93d02654569f288.jpg","text":"Wolk vervolgde zijn reis.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43557/size6/63e507ee46560ce0bcc3210cb6af2796.jpg","text":"In de rivier springend, danste een vis.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43558/size6/85ba6464282111053c9cb5bbc4f763ff.jpg","text":"Wolk begeleidde de dans van de vis met regen.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/43559/size6/d48f6808d9fec6e280477699dabac8ad.jpg","text":"Hij kwam hier om te reizen. Daarom reisde hij verder, van het blauw vandaan.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":13,"words":121}}